{"tid":1431251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想多謝喺我屋企附近度做文宣嘅每一個人","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:34:52.000Z","uid":267983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f3a64cbf9b77e41e2a96cdbc434370785804f82","tid":1431251,"uid":267983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"由7月初我嗰區開始有人起連儂牆，我自己都遊行前有去貼，但返黎就唔知會左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後間中西營盤站出口對出都有人用紙皮起牆，但好多時都過唔到一晚就消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，到應該係前日定琴日有人喺巴士站貼元朗啲文宣。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我睇唔到內容，我想話你地知你哋嘅努力係冇白費到嫁。圖一係7月7號嘅連儂牆，圖二係今日啱啱影巴士站嘅文宣。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MXWzo58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMXWzo58.jpg&h=b678fc32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rPk8txY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPk8txY.jpg&h=62ec3adc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fba782528398ff371c8ed55149fd70a74c511034","tid":1431251,"uid":267983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"希望你曾經參與過起牆或者做文宣嘅會睇到啦，如果有需要睇牆，我作為附近居民落黎幫下手，其實都無咩所謂同好願意嫁。"},{"pid":"47153937aa5a605d38747cb9d99aa75910d48b68","tid":1431251,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OxsSaTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxsSaTE.jpg&h=600a03aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xttmOFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxttmOFk.png&h=78ecfc5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8UqMfko.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UqMfko.jpg&h=70a32a12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3V8tFp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht